[normal]3.2.1
[normal]              
[normal]The original consultation document set out the Government's belief that the existing rules surrounding the taxation of members of a Limited Liability Partnership (LLP
[normal]),
[normal] are effectively open to abuse. It is stated that this produces "unfairness in the tax s
[normal]ystem". 
[normal]&#xa0;
