[normal]n fact, somewhat
[normal] 
[normal]heavy handed and disproportionate. Furthermore, 
[normal]it is likely that
[normal] the measures will, in fact, put partnerships at a disadvantage when compared to other business vehicles available, such as a company, for example.  
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3.2.3 
[normal]              
